(945, 1, '2018-05-24 01:20:46', '2018-05-24 05:20:46', 'yes you can claim rebate for HRA and housing loan intt. and principal repayment both.', 'Can i claim rebate for HRA and housing loan ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'can-i-claim-rebate-for-hra-and-housing-loan', '', '', '2018-05-24 01:20:46', '2018-05-24 05:20:46', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?post_type=loan&#038;p=945', 0, 'loan', '', 0),
(946, 1, '2018-05-24 01:21:33', '2018-05-24 05:21:33', 'If you have availed one housing loan, you can claim deduction of intt. payment upto 1.50 lakh in a year and a deduction u/s 80-c of upto rs. 1.00 lakh. But if you availed another housing loan on another housing property. then you have to choose yourself that which property is to be shown as self occupied property and which property is to be shown an let out property. the total intt. payment on the deemed let out property is deductible from the gross total income. but you have to add the deemed rental income in your total income.', 'If i have availed one housing loan and now availing another housing loan can i claim rebate for both the loans ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'if-i-have-availed-one-housing-loan-and-now-availing-another-housing-loan-can-i-claim-rebate-for-both-the-loans', '', '', '2018-05-24 01:21:33', '2018-05-24 05:21:33', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?post_type=loan&#038;p=946', 0, 'loan', '', 0),
(947, 1, '2018-05-24 01:22:07', '2018-05-24 05:22:07', 'Interst payable by an assessee in respect of funds borrowed for the acquisition or construction of a house property and pertaining to a period prior to the previous year in which such property has been acquired or constructed, to the extent it is not allowed as a deduction under any other provision of the act, will be deducted in five equal annual instalments, commencing from the previous year in which the house is acquired or constructed.', 'What is the tax benefit on the interest on pre-construction period ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-the-tax-benefit-on-the-interest-on-pre-construction-period', '', '', '2018-05-24 01:22:07', '2018-05-24 05:22:07', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?post_type=loan&#038;p=947', 0, 'loan', '', 0),
(948, 1, '2018-05-24 01:22:46', '2018-05-24 05:22:46', 'Interest of pre-construction period is deductible in five equal instalments. the first instalment is deductible in the year in which construction of property is completed or in which property is acquired.', 'What is pre construction period ?', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'what-is-pre-construction-period', '', '', '2018-05-24 01:22:46', '2018-05-24 05:22:46', '', 0, 'http://txdigital.ddns.net/dev/rim/wordpress/?post_type=loan&#038;p=948', 0, 'loan', '', 0),
